+/****************************************************************************/
+/* Starts the RISC processor.                                               */
+/*                                                                          */
+/* Assumes the CPU starting address has already been set.                   */
+/*                                                                          */
+/* Returns:                                                                 */
+/*   Nothing.                                                               */
